SUMMARY:Oregon City Winter Farmers Market
DESCRIPTION:The Farmers Market has moved to Clackamas Community College in Oregon City.  You’ll find us in Green Lot #1\, near the corner of S Beavercreek Road and Clairmont Drive. Click here to learn more about the new location.\n\nAbout the Market\nOur year-round Farmers Market celebrates the best of our region—featuring local growers\, farmers\, ranchers\, bakers\, artisan food makers\, wineries\, distilleries\, cideries\, and crafters.\nClick here for our interactive vendor map.\nDuring the holiday season\, look for artisan gifts\, wreaths\, and greenery.\n\n\nWinter Market Schedule (2025–2026)\nOur Winter Market runs Saturdays\, 10:00am–2:00pm. We operate outdoors\, rain or shine\, with plenty of parking and ADA access\n\n\n\nMarket Dates:\n\nNovember: 1\, 8\, 15\, 22 (Harvest Market)\nClosed: November 29 (Thanksgiving weekend)\nDecember: 6\, 13\, 20 (Holiday Market)\nClosed: December 27 & January 3\nJanuary: 10\, 24\nFebruary: 7\, 21\nMarch: 7\, 21\nApril: 4\, 18\n\n\n\nSNAP & Double Up Food Bucks\nWe proudly accept SNAP cards\, with up to a $20 Double Up Food Buck match per market visit—thanks to grant support from Farmers Market Fund.\n\n\n\n\nWeather & Updates\nThe market runs rain or shine\, but may close early or cancel in case of severe weather.\nVisit our website for the latest updates\, attending vendors and event info. Or\, sign up for our newsletter:\n \n\n\n\nSubscribe to Our Mailing ListKeep up to date with the latest market news\, events\, and vendors! \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nThank you for supporting local growers and producers.
URL:https://orcityfarmersmarket.com/event/oregon-city-winter-farmers-market-14/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:Oregon City Farmers Market\, Clackamas Community College\, Green Lot #1\, near corner of Beavercreek Road and Clairmont Drive\, Oregon City\, OR\, 97045\, United States
CATEGORIES:Market
